WEBVTT

00:00:53,429 --> 00:00:56,229
Once in a while when I wake up


00:00:58,100 --> 00:01:00,360
I find myself crying.


00:01:01,771 --> 00:01:05,471
The dream I must have had I can never recall.


00:01:06,067 --> 00:01:07,427
But...


00:01:08,861 --> 00:01:12,113
the sensation that I've lost something


00:01:12,114 --> 00:01:15,514
lingers for a long time after I wake up.


00:01:23,542 --> 00:01:25,742
I'm always searching


00:01:25,753 --> 00:01:28,373
for something, for someone.


